5. Policy
Add Policy
POST http://localhost:8080/api/policies
Valid JSON Body: (use existing customerId, coverageId, policyTypeId)

{
  "policyNumber": "POL12345",
  "premium": 5000.0,
  "customerId": 1,
  "coverageId": 1,
  "policyTypeId": 1
}


‚ùå Add Policy (Empty policyNumber)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/policies
Invalid JSON Body:

{
  "policyNumber": "",
  "premium": 5000.0,
  "customerId": 1,
  "coverageId": 1,
  "policyTypeId": 1
}
Expected Error: Error: Policy number is required.

Get All Policies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/policies

Get Policy by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/policies/1

Get Policies by Customer ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/policies/customer/1

